{"tid":288116,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紅雨凌晨襲港3個鐘逾2,600次閃電","createTime":"2017-06-18T03:25:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-18T04:20:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"23ef676799938ca1e853fe4f924dfcea2edcaae4","tid":288116,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T03:25:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20060211&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170618\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20060211%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170618&d=s30LARp%2FNBXgucy0VtagdPjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=68b313d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20060211%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170618&h=c5ce8799\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20060211&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170618</a><br />\n<br />\n紅雨凌晨襲港<br />\n3個鐘逾2,600次閃電<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】因受到一道低壓槽影響，昨凌晨時分本港出現大雨，天文台先後發出黃雨及紅雨警告，當中市區及西貢錄得超過30毫米雨量，而港島部分地區、南丫島及長洲更錄得超過100毫米雨量。其間本港多區雷電交加，有居於南丫島的居民索性關掉電總掣，有人指被震耳雷聲驚醒，亦有網民誇張地形容「閃到宇宙大爆炸」、「好像地球裂開咁，好似明日之後咁」。<br />\n<br />\n究竟閃電次數有多少呢？根據天文台網站數據，昨晚由凌晨1時至凌晨4時，3小時內，本港境內雲對地閃電次數共2,659次，其中近6成發生於港島及九龍區，有1,546次；新界東亦有893次。<br />\n<br />\n97年主權移交至今，香港前進還是倒退？「蘋果」與你細數廿載風雨。<br />\n【回歸二十年】專頁：&nbsp;<a href=\"http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhksar20.appledaily.com.hk&d=s30LARp%2FNBXgucy0VtagdPjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=47dc2ea2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk</a>￼"},{"pid":"1351865da910001917a9a96fe76d70749822071d","tid":288116,"uid":113074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T03:29:38.000Z","msg":"大交合又夜晚放雷暴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dea